    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> diced chicken breast </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 6-8 min or until golden</p><p>Once golden, remove the chicken and set aside, reserve the pan</p><p>Tip: It’s okay if the chicken's a little pink on the inside, it’ll get cooked more later</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
