    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat and add 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> of the <strong>garlic & herb butter </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Once melted, add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp] </span><strong>flour </strong>and stir with a wooden spoon for 1-2 min or until a sandy paste forms</p><p>Gradually stir in the <strong>creamy stock</strong>, a little at a time (to prevent lumps forming)</p>",
