            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sprinkle the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs</strong> all over the farfalle</p><p>Dollop the <strong>remaining garlic & herb butter </strong>over the breadcrumbs and put the dish in the oven for 12-15 min or until golden and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chicken breast kyiv pasta bake</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>courgette batons </strong>to a baking tray with a squeeze of <strong>lemon</strong> juice, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and put the tray in the oven for 12-15 min or until cooked through</p>",
